  "pr": {
    "title": "refactor: split monolith into search/identity/checkout packages (closes #1188)",
    "body": "Splits the legacy `app/` monolith into three top-level packages so we can ship them independently. Mostly mechanical: imports rewritten, files moved, and per-package test suites moved alongside their package. No behavior change is intended; the public CLI commands are unchanged.\n\nFixes #1188. CI fully green; staging smoke clean.",
